<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/privacy.css">

<h1>Change profile</h1>
<p>In this demo site you are logged as a <span>BUYER ACCOUNT</span> but if you click the button below, you are logged in an <span>ADMIN ACCOUNT</span> the admin account is able to post content in the store page</p>
<button id="adminModeBtn" onclick="toggleAdminMode()">Change account</button>

<div id="adminSection" style="display:none;">
    <h2>Add New Product</h2>
    <form id="addProductForm" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/Store/AddProduct">
        <label for="productName">Product Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="productName" name="productName" required><br><br>

        <label for="productInfo">Product Info:</label>
        <textarea id="productInfo" name="productInfo" required></textarea><br><br>

        <label for="productPrice">Product Price:</label>
        <input type="number" id="productPrice" name="productPrice" required><br><br>

        <label for="productImage">Product Image:</label>
        <input type="file" id="productImage" name="productImage" accept="image/*" required><br><br>

        <button type="submit">Add Product</button>
    </form>

</div>
